          <p style={{ color: "#6b7280", fontSize: 15, marginBottom: 36, fontFamily: "'Libre Franklin', sans-serif", lineHeight: 1.6 }}>Bridging charities and companies for meaningful social investment partnerships.</p>
          <div style={{ display: "flex", gap: 16, justifyContent: "center" }}>
            {([
              { r: "charity" as Role, title: "I'm a Charity", desc: "Create project proposals and find company partners", accent: "#0f2942" },
              { r: "company" as Role, title: "I'm a Company", desc: "Register skills and browse projects to support", accent: "#16a34a" },
